data.description: Beautiful newer 4-sided brick upgraded home. Located in Stockbridge's Austin Park subdivision, waiting for its new owner! You will fall totally in love with the open-concept floorplan. The oversized family room, lovely gourmet kitchen, and upgraded appliances are just some awe-inspiring moments you will experience. The roof is only 4 years old. Washer and Dryer come with the home. A home that is not only perfect for you and your family but spaciously enough to entertain for the holidays. Relax in the ensuite bath after a hard day at work. The secondary bedrooms are very generous in size, and the kids or guests will spend hours enjoying their incredible spaces. You will enjoy spending time in your lovely backyard, which has a shed for storage. This home is located near shopping, restaurants, and highways.
